{"tid":2026942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"估唔到黃色經濟圈,本來只係一把刀仔可以變核彈!!","createTime":"2020-05-21T09:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T15:16:40.000Z","uid":259520,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2a40cdc24509b1e1f7f9d9612c5944d2b76bfd9","tid":2026942,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:02:31.000Z","msg":"國安法一立就可即時完成香港中共一齊攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/05/21/HK2005210008.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2020%2F05%2F21%2FHK2005210008.htm&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=17d6e95d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/05/21/HK2005210008.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n真係估唔到黃色經濟圈,本來只係一把刀仔(可能只係樹支).<br />\n竟然可以變核彈.<br />\n只要用國安法一講黃色經濟圈犯法.<br />\n就可以證明香自由經濟體系,完全玩完.<br />\n<br />\n因為當個人消費意都話犯法既時候.<br />\n商人在港從商只要支持反共既政客, 隨時拉得.<br />\n當然中共中定話個別事件, <br />\n不過之後永遠有一把刀在佢地(商家)頭上.<br />\n不支持中共就可以斬落來.<br />\n香港經濟股市正式等收皮.(當然延後性,外資會慢慢走)<br />\n<br />\n呢單新聞加立23條同國安法.<br />\n可以一齊在外國煲大佢."},{"pid":"2d9cf131fea9021e652decf2d17764453854d5a0","tid":2026942,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"0b3f8c36d0a676ec50dd3b01eaebd3fb2888f9b4","tid":2026942,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:03:58.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n[香港文化] 上連登打正字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026832</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d74f7d2a76bdd3417a40707e71d46ae96f5e8c07","tid":2026942,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:06:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3c276cb95142668ff7d4e9842c386b55aff862a","tid":2026942,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"估唔到仲有威力過街頭抗爭"},{"pid":"30d4af4e14960e5cf5ceda67edc922ab0000f094","tid":2026942,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d74f7d2a76bdd3417a40707e71d46ae96f5e8c07","tid":2026942,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:06:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"唔係靠人幫. 而係D外國商家唔可以再只搵錢.<br />\n<br />\n當中共叫你出錢買佢D人民幣債.唔到你唔買.<br />\n當個人消費意慾都可以話犯法.<br />\n唔買佢D人民幣債卷,已經可以係犯法.<br />\n<br />\n外商仲有幾多覺得在香港投資會係安全???<br />\n安全性成疑有仲會唔會增加投資.<br />\n甚至撤出或減少."},{"pid":"1b5085eef2e21131baa8c978ee68aed052a2a801","tid":2026942,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3ea8e829ec88b511ffe98d9bb23a774034fe5f","tid":2026942,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:13:08.000Z","msg":"中共啲傻西又真係中晒計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c5ec69eeae9ab2e02c6b9daf62ce63b4490ae3","tid":2026942,"uid":331389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"用返民建聯攬炒banner嘛"}]}